{"tid":1837464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28號先封關？太遲喇，已經好近直線爆發既階段","createTime":"2020-01-23T15:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T04:57:46.000Z","uid":40250,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e40458645a4d8745309a2fd6ced1de02fe2c7fb","tid":1837464,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"武漢已經全面爆發，以十萬計既case<br />\n要封關就要盡快"},{"pid":"aaff1762ad83eedde06b4b9bec31e2701af5e15f","tid":1837464,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"嘗試整合香港醫療問題，係時候向正苦爭取合理訴求<br />\n<br />\n立即封關<br />\n加重本地醫療資源（醫院&amp;醫學）<br />\n加重本地人口老化帶來資源缺乏<br />\n中醫資格香港讀到<br />\n取消每日150 專才 人口政策<br />\n<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"53821866ae880b03c812b93276f585166be8dbef","tid":1837464,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaMG3yu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaMG3yu.png&h=57e8d91e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3d5ec9022ca52350909f4fb0dcfa78c9f572bbc","tid":1837464,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"Dllm"},{"pid":"58d8fed51e86e3cd893bb946ef93b7bd74025bd6","tid":1837464,"uid":28446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"廢柴港共永遠都係慢10拍<br />\n一早撤回就無事<br />\n一早封關就無事"},{"pid":"d5472ab7374bcda791572e225eef4f7b112d36f6","tid":1837464,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"做酒店既會唔會肯為左封關放棄生意？而係照放佢地黎住，係酒店傳播病毒？<br />\n<br />\n做開中國客保險既，會唔會為左生意而唔幫佢地落香港，避免佢地係社區傳染？<br />\n<br />\n同樣做地產/商場/貿易，會唔會肯犧牲半年既營業額而讚成封關？<br />\n<br />\n唔會，一定唔會，每個人都為左私利賺盡最後一分錢然後走佬。唔理今次疫症為香港社會帶黎幾多人命損失同醫療開支。"},{"pid":"a322d2c42afb680eec4476b801c14da18c1b490e","tid":1837464,"uid":50878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5472ab7374bcda791572e225eef4f7b112d36f6","tid":1837464,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"做酒店既會唔會肯為左封關放棄生意？而係照放佢地黎住，係酒店傳播病毒？<br />\n<br />\n做開中國客保險既，會唔會為左生意而唔幫佢地落香港，避免佢地係社區傳染？<br />\n<br />\n同樣做地產/商場/貿易，會唔會肯犧牲半年既營業額而讚成封關？<br />\n<br />\n唔會，一定唔會，每個人都為左私利賺盡最後一分錢然後走佬。唔理今次疫症為香港社會帶黎幾多人命損失同醫療開支。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"true<br />\n<br />\n身邊全部生意人<br />\n<br />\n無人care過肺炎，全部人個腦都係諗緊賺緊幾多錢<br />\n同埋點樣賺更多錢<br />\n<br />\n搞到我每次上連登好似入左平行世界咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}